data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming home yours! Pride of ownership is evident throughout!! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home features all bedrooms on the second floor, a stone fireplace, quarter-acre lot, and a giant primary bedroom closet! Recent updates and features include: painting throughout with modern color scheme, hvac serviced and repaired, dryer vent and ductwork inspected and cleaned, propane tank will remain (not leased). Security system to include camera/light above the garage and doorbell, tv mount, metal shelving and hooks in garage DO NOT CONVEY. Schedule a viewing to experience the warmth and character that await you!! Sellers need to close end of January 2024, may move up to earlier in January - flexible buyer needed!
